OL,7,FThe NAO report, published on Monday,
OL,8,Fsaid the impacts of dangerous cladding
OL,9,F"have extended far beyond the
OL,10,Fimmediate victims of the Grenfell
OL,11,Ffire, with many people suffering
OL,12,Fsignificant financial and emotional
OL,13,Fdistress".
OL,15,FIt noted that on top of living with
OL,16,Fthe fear of fire, there have been
OL,17,Fcostly bills for remediation and some
OL,18,Fresidents have paid for so-called
OL,19,Fwaking watches to patrol buildings
OL,20,Fwhile waiting for cladding to be
OL,21,Fremoved.
