OL,7,FThe NAO said the Ministry of Housing,
OL,8,FCommunities and Local Government
OL,9,F(MHCLG) has estimated somewhere
OL,10,Fbetween 9,000 and 12,000 buildings
OL,11,Fwill need remediating ` made safe.
OL,13,FThe latest official figures, up to the
OL,14,Fend of September 2024, showed there
OL,15,Fwere 4,821 residential buildings of at
OL,16,Fleast 11 metres in height identified
OL,17,Fwith unsafe cladding, up by 50 since
OL,18,Fprevious month.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/19
