OL,7,FThis total is thought to account for
OL,8,Fmore than a quarter of a million
OL,9,Findividual homes.
OL,11,FOf the 4,821 buildings identified,
OL,12,Fonly half had either started or
OL,13,Fcompleted remediation works.
OL,15,FThe NAO report stated: "Pace has been
OL,16,Fa persistent concern and remediation
OL,17,Fwithin the portfolio is progressing
OL,18,Fmore slowly than MHCLG expected."
