OL,7,FThe department's modelling estimates
OL,8,Fan end date of 2035 for completing
OL,9,Fcladding remediation, but the NAO
OL,10,Fwarned this will be "challenging to
OL,11,Fachieve".
OL,13,FAmong its recommendations, the
OL,14,Fwatchdog said the department "should
OL,15,Fpublish a target date by which it
OL,16,Fexpects all affected buildings to be
OL,17,Fremediated based on its understanding
OL,18,Fof the number of buildings to be
OL,19,Fremediated and the speed at which it
OL,20,Fexpects building owners and developers
OL,21,Fto complete works".
