OL,15,Fpaid by developers on new
OL,16,Fdevelopments, is not expected to start
OL,17,Funtil autumn 2025 at the earliest and
OL,18,FMHCLG is yet to confirm payment
OL,19,Fmechanisms, the NAO said.
